00:14:49,256 --> 00:14:50,390
Is that the wind?

332
00:14:50,424 --> 00:14:52,459
Eugeo: You picked
the right path!

333
00:14:52,492 --> 00:14:54,594
We’re almost to the entrance!

334
00:14:54,628 --> 00:14:56,296
Alice: Wait! Be careful,

335
00:14:56,330 --> 00:14:58,332
