00:16:42,069 --> 00:16:43,537
( Alice shudders )

351
00:16:57,784 --> 00:16:58,718
Kirito: No, wait!

352
00:17:12,399 --> 00:17:13,367
Eugeo: Alice!

353
00:17:13,400 --> 00:17:15,235
( Boys gasp )

354
00:17:17,604 --> 00:17:19,005
( Alice gasps )

355
00:17:24,778 --> 00:17:27,681
